-- Cardiff Signs Striker Craig Bellamy From Liverpool for Two Years
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-08-10T13:47:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-10/cardiff-signs-striker-craig-bellamy-from-liverpool-for-two-years.html
Cardiff City signed Wales striker
 Craig Bellamy  from Liverpool, the second-tier English club said
on its website.  Bellamy signed a two-year contract to return to Cardiff,
where he spent the 2010-11 season on loan from Manchester City.
The 33-year-old scored nine goals in 37 appearances last season
after joining Liverpool from Manchester City.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
